                     <interp inst="t18470614-1537-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp> for stealing 1 cart, value 6<hi rend="italic">l</hi>.; the property of <persName id="t18470614-name-1136" type="victimName">
